## 🏛️ 2. Architectural Design Patterns & SOLID Principles
* **Principal Engineer Persona**: Write clean, production-ready, performant, and self-documenting code.
* **Separation of Concerns**: Separate business logic (services/context) from visual rendering layers (components/pages).
* **Styling Integrity**: Maintain the common visual theme system. Do not write ad-hoc style sheets for minor changes. Reuse design tokens, tailwind layers, and context properties.
* **Single Responsibility**: Do not bloat single components. Split large components (like long forms or dialog panels) into modular subcomponents or custom react hooks.

